{"tid":2260611,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"廖啟智智叔近況落魄？疑街頭擺攤賣衣，形象邋遢不修邊幅","createTime":"2020-10-27T16:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T10:03:43.000Z","uid":68916,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d4ee5bf34efd269eb4b6b9d9965515d9b71de0e2","tid":2260611,"uid":68916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p1-tt.byteimg.com/origin/pgc-image/4bb6754e27764f8db6b125a9db81a264\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp1-tt.byteimg.com%2Forigin%2Fpgc-image%2F4bb6754e27764f8db6b125a9db81a264&h=4fd740fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p1-tt.byteimg.com/origin/pgc-image/888ce8325cd64ed3afa06d7e153c218c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp1-tt.byteimg.com%2Forigin%2Fpgc-image%2F888ce8325cd64ed3afa06d7e153c218c&h=75d11896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p6-tt.byteimg.com/origin/pgc-image/9cfc309f9cda4f3aa049487909fdbec1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp6-tt.byteimg.com%2Forigin%2Fpgc-image%2F9cfc309f9cda4f3aa049487909fdbec1&h=c5c68196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網友在社交平台上分享了一段偶遇到香港知名演員廖啟智的視頻。視頻中的廖啟智疑似在街頭擺攤賣衣服，引起了不少網友的注意。<br />\n<br />\n當天，廖啟智穿著一件黃色條紋的POLO衫，將袖子擼上去露出手臂，衣著不整。一頭未經打理的捲髮顯得凌亂邋遢，眼袋明顯，素顏出鏡還有些滄桑，看上去不修邊幅。<br />\n<br />\n廖啟智坐在一個賣衣服的小攤中間，肩上背著一個斜挎包，還時不時招呼著旁人挑選衣服，就像是在街頭市場擺攤賣衣服的小商販。"},{"pid":"f1804ef4182c8d4e775e12d69f03542f58c60bbc","tid":2260611,"uid":178290,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:55:48.000Z","msg":"乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1e639fab995d9da0a9e3d5d6c109aff782ba72","tid":2260611,"uid":105661,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"劇照咋嘛？"},{"pid":"298df7d20537191bdb8e52574452de75b2f5c7c6","tid":2260611,"uid":98473,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"fc左先啦 電影花絮黎<br />\n宜家成個連登好似d藍絲group咁"}